src:
Hasil Pemanasan Moto3 Malaysia: Albert Arenas Memimpin
03 Nov 2019, 08:16 by Bola.net
Bola.net - Pebalap Angel Nieto Team, Albert Arenas, sukses mencatat waktu tercepat dalam sesi pemanasan (WUP) Moto3 Malaysia di Sirkuit Sepang pada Minggu (3/11/2019).
Pebalap Spanyol ini diikuti oleh pebalap Leopard Racing, Marcos Ramirez, di posisi kedua dan pebalap Kommerling Gresini, Garbierl Rodrigo, di posisi ketiga.
Sementara itu posisi keempat dan kelima masing-masing ditempati oleh pebalap Mugen Race, Andrea Migno, dan pebalap Leopard Racing lainnya, Lorenzo dalla Porta.
Berikut hasil WUP Moto3 Malaysia 2019.
text:
Malaysian Moto3 Warming Results: Albert Arenas Leads
Nov 3 2019, 08:16 by Bola.net
Bola.net - Angel Nieto Team rider, Albert Arenas, successfully recorded the fastest time in the Malaysian Moto3 warm-up session (WUP) at the Sepang Circuit on Sunday (3/11/2019).
The Spaniard was followed by Leopard Racing driver Marcos Ramirez in second place and Kommerling Gresini, Garbierl Rodrigo, in third position.
Meanwhile the fourth and fifth positions were each occupied by Mugen Race riders, Andrea Migno, and other Leopard Racing riders, Lorenzo dalla Porta.
Following are the results of the 2019 Malaysian Moto3 WUP.
